---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Mad Learning Lab — Evaluation and learning systems for nonprofits"
  description="Lean evaluation and learning systems for nonprofits — built for both leadership that needs to prove impact and staff already stretched thin."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <span class="eyebrow">Evaluation &amp; Learning Systems for Nonprofits</span>
    <h1 class="hero-headline">Good missions deserve <em>good systems</em>.</h1>
    <div class="hero-body">
      <p class="hero-lede">
        I bridge the gap between executive ambition and operational reality.
      </p>
      <p>
        Mad Learning Lab builds lean evaluation and learning systems for nonprofits — the kind
        a busy program manager can run on a Tuesday afternoon, and a board chair can read in
        five minutes. Most nonprofits live between two pressures that never quite meet:
        leadership that needs to prove impact, and staff already stretched thin. I sit between
        them, and design for both.
      </p>
      <p>
        My work is research-grounded and time-honest. I bring the rigor of formal methods and
        the practicality of someone who has sat inside nonprofits long enough to know what
        works.
      </p>
      <p class="hero-refrain">When I leave, the work stays.</p>
    </div>
    <a href="/contact" class="cta">
      Get in touch
      <span class="cta-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
    </a>
  </section>
</Base>
